# Local-only team coordination memory (NOT committed; mirrored to OneDrive).
# Contains: lead kickoff prompts, per-lead handoffs, session summaries, story
# candidates, cross-lead coordination threads, interview-story repo, plus
# project docs (PRD source, lesson sketches, demo plans) under .project/<slug>/docs/.
# None of it ships to the public mirror or the partner's submission. See
# WORKTREE_PATTERNS.md "OneDrive mirroring" section and
# scripts/setup-onedrive-mirror.sh.
/.project/

# Claude Code agent definitions + skills + settings — local-only (OneDrive).
# Slash commands /aria, /bram, /cleo, /tate are tied to this machine's setup;
# other machines pick them up via OneDrive sync, not git.
/.claude/

